{"tid":2283033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點做？制裁晒成個議會","createTime":"2020-11-12T09:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T09:26:35.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a2af3090c98253ca28ef48535c491d7d3eb0e8f","tid":2283033,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158700496422357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158700496422357&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByqGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=f6f95ef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158700496422357</a><br />\n<br />\n仲好意思問我可以點做，一早叫話制裁晒成個議會，所有議員 ban 銀行戶口當戰犯，議員薪津一概當犯罪所得，全部處理議員薪津既人一概當洗黑錢，係班人貪小便宜想靠議會出糧，考慮都唔考慮之嘛<br />\n<br />\n成個垃圾會食穀種咪最好。以後香港邊個再敢做議員，成世走唔出大灣區同伊朗。以後唔伊去日本浸溫泉啦，東莞浸飽佢。<br />\n<br />\n又要求美軍火力支援，自己又行入射程範圍，要求對方就住唔好傷及無辜？"},{"pid":"db9e3906fec3565bf0609ee11b50679d682f1b78","tid":2283033,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:26:35.000Z","msg":"咩都唔好講住 po個ig story定下驚先"}]}